{"tid":406011,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足去過印尼參觀雨林或睇科莫多龍？","createTime":"2017-09-19T10:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T02:32:21.000Z","uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20ec7a035a1659dc186354d03f404bf598ebce46","tid":406011,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:00:37.000Z","msg":"細佬由細到大都好中意動物，成日去動物園。到而家出來做野，叫做有少少經濟能力，就想去睇下真正的熱帶雨林同科莫多龍。<br />\n<br />\n有沒有手足去過印尼探討過大自然？<br />\n<br />\n我知道科莫多龍係住響島上，而唔係雨林，咁有冇辦法一次過去哂？"},{"pid":"824765b652565e7178b252d2dab195b0941715b6","tid":406011,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:10:02.000Z","msg":"順便玩埋印尼雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9140c70e5707adfaafdc284318a0b04796e627","tid":406011,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:16:09.000Z","msg":"旅遊保一般包唔包？<br />\n<br />\n咬一啖唔係講笑<br />\n<br />\n淨係菌都多到喊"},{"pid":"36492061e6d1fe4e3a21d4314ad661dd0457328b","tid":406011,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順便玩埋印尼雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4233cc1943720febc3d79660c1989dac8c00ea6f","tid":406011,"uid":14911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"上年去左睇科莫多龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好震撼，差d見到佢搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但睇科莫多龍得三個島有得睇，個d都唔係雨林黎"},{"pid":"f47b9d578b81